Polokwane Squash Club will join the Masjiensquash Limpopo Roadshow by hosting two of South Africa s best squash players JP Brits and Christo Potgieter tomorrow (Wednesday) evening. Local organiser Johan Bouwer invites everyone interested to attend the event at the local squash court. He also advises that arriving before 18:00 would help secure seats as entry is free. The two players will share valuable tips and advice on how to improve your game where after they will play an exhibition match starting at 18:30. Brits and Potgieter whose highest national rankings are fifth and third respectively, are both qualified coaches and have also participated successfully on international level. For more information contact Robby Vilar on 082 883 2255. Story: RC Myburgh &gt;&gt;rc.observer@gmail.com